                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; incipits and headings of the texts;
                           short postscripts to the Gospels of Matthew and Mark; chapter numbers (in
                           the “tituli”), titles and the word mǝʿrāf; elements of the punctuation
                           signs and Ethiopic numbers.
 On the incipit page of each Gospel, a
                           few lines are rubricated (in groups of two lines, alternating with black
                           lines).</seg>
                     </handNote>
